This resource collection provide methods to manage Room Types.

Room Type type is `room_type`.

## Room Type Attributes

|Field|Type|Description|
|-----|----|-----------|
|id|`UUID`|Room Type Unique Identificator|
|title|`STRING`|Room Type title|
|count_of_rooms|`INTEGER`|Count of rooms under that room type|
|hotel_id|`UUID`|Reference to parent Hotel|

```
{
    "type": "room_type",
    "relationships": {
        "hotel": {
            "data": {
                "type": "hotel",
                "id": "4d981378-9184-494b-927d-c11fe74abae8"
            }
        }
    },
    "id": "c0d3f3d0-ae57-4b3d-9014-bf143e094765",
    "attributes": {
        "id": "c0d3f3d0-ae57-4b3d-9014-bf143e094765",
        "title": "Test Room Type",
        "count_of_rooms": 1
    }
}
```

This resource collection provide methods to manage connected Channels.

Channel type is `channel`.

## Channel Attributes

|Field|Type|Description|
|-----|----|-----------|
|id|`UUID`|Room Type Unique Identificator|
|hotel_id|`UUID`|Reference to parent Hotel|
|title|`STRING`|Rate Plan title|
|is_active|`BOOLEAN`|Active marker|

```
{
    "data": {
        "type": "channel",
        "relationships": {
            "hotel": {
                "data": {
                    "type": "hotel",
                    "id": "4d981378-9184-494b-927d-c11fe74abae8"
                }
            }
        },
        "id": "5ecd5e27-b39c-4cbb-a89a-178c5d8c55f6",
        "attributes": {
            "title": "test",
            "is_active": true,
            "id": "5ecd5e27-b39c-4cbb-a89a-178c5d8c55f6"
        }
    }
}
```

This resource collection provide methods to manage Currency Profiles.

Currency Profile type is `currency_profile`.

## Currency Profile Attributes

|Field|Type|Description|
|-----|----|-----------|
|id|`UUID`|Room Type Unique Identificator|
|hotel_id|`UUID`|Reference to parent Hotel|
|currency|`STRING`|Currency ISO code|
|is_manual|`BOOLEAN`|Marker represents manual rate or not|
|exchange_rate|`DECIMAL`|Exchange Rate to base hotel currency|

```
{
    "data": {
        "type": "channel",
        "relationships": {
            "hotel": {
                "data": {
                    "type": "hotel",
                    "id": "4d981378-9184-494b-927d-c11fe74abae8"
                }
            }
        },
        "id": "5ecd5e27-b39c-4cbb-a89a-178c5d8c55f6",
        "attributes": {
            "title": "test",
            "is_active": true,
            "id": "5ecd5e27-b39c-4cbb-a89a-178c5d8c55f6"
        }
    }
}
```
